'''Braze''' was a shortened term for [[brown]] haze. It was a kind of air pollution found in [[Cloud City/Legends|Cloud City]], and it was a major byproduct of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire's]] harvest of metals and [[Tibanna/Legends|tibanna]] gas from the [[Planet/Legends|planet's]] [[Rethen/Legends|rethin]] core.

